---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Agora">
    <main class="container mx-auto px-6 py-32 relative z-10 min-h-[60vh]">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-text-color border-b border-black/10 pb-4 mb-12">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <div class="space-y-10 text-lg text-slate-800">
                <p class="text-base text-slate-500"><strong>Last updated:</strong> August 03, 2025</p>

                <section class="space-y-4">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-semibold text-text-color">1. Introduction</h2>
                    <p class="leading-relaxed">
                        Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how Agora Bot ("Agora," "we," "us," or "our") collects, 
                        uses, and discloses information when you use our Discord bot and its related services.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class="space-y-4">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-semibold text-text-color">2. Information We Collect</h2>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-outside space-y-3 pl-5 leading-relaxed">
                        <li><strong>Discord User IDs</strong> – Used to identify you in debates, track Elo ratings, and manage personalized settings.</li>
                        <li><strong>Discord Server IDs</strong> – Used to manage server-specific settings and debates.</li>
                        <li><strong>Limited Message Content</strong> – Processed only to identify bot commands and debate responses. Not stored permanently unless required for a core feature.</li>
                        <li><strong>Elo Ratings & Debate Statistics</strong> – Stored for leaderboard functionality.</li>
                        <li><strong>Non-Personal Usage Data</strong> – Collected in anonymized form to improve the bot.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="space-y-4">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-semibold text-text-color">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-outside space-y-3 pl-5 leading-relaxed">
                        <li>To operate and maintain Agora’s debate features.</li>
                        <li>To improve and develop new features.</li>
                        <li>To personalize user experiences and maintain statistics.</li>
                        <li>For moderation and security purposes.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="space-y-4">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-semibold text-text-color">4. Data Storage and Security</h2>
                    <p class="leading-relaxed">
                        Data is stored on secure servers with reasonable safeguards. While we strive for protection, no method is 100% secure.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class="space-y-4">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-semibold text-text-color">5. Sharing Your Information</h2>
                    <p class="leading-relaxed">We do not sell or trade personal information. Data may be shared only with:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-outside space-y-3 pl-5 leading-relaxed">
                        <li>Service providers performing functions on our behalf.</li>
                        <li>Authorities when required by law.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="space-y-4">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-semibold text-text-color">6. Your Data Rights</h2>
                    <p class="leading-relaxed">You may request access, correction, or deletion of your data at any time via <a href="mailto:support@agorabot.app" class="text-accent-color underline hover:text-primary-color transition-colors">support@agorabot.app</a>.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="space-y-4">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-semibold text-text-color">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
                    <p class="leading-relaxed">Agora is not intended for users under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="space-y-4">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-semibold text-text-color">8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
                    <p class="leading-relaxed">We may update this Privacy Policy periodically and will update the “Last updated” date accordingly.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="space-y-4">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-semibold text-text-color">9. Contact Us</h2>
                    <p class="leading-relaxed">Email: <a href="mailto:support@agorabot.app" class="text-accent-color underline hover:text-primary-color transition-colors">support@agorabot.app</a></p>
                    <p class="leading-relaxed">
                        Discord: <a href="https://discord.gg/Tev6uSYBH5" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent-color underline hover:text-primary-color transition-colors">https://discord.gg/Tev6uSYBH5</a>
                    </p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>
